{"tid":1795640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市民入稟就831衝突向警方索償　明年6月再訊","createTime":"2019-12-24T05:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T08:26:06.000Z","uid":258208,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1b1b97b49c9c079408e5649ee0dc215607afb235","tid":1795640,"uid":258208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:16:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】8月31日太子站衝突有市民指在站內被警員毆打，早前入稟區域法院向警務處處長索償，並申請命令要求披露站內閉路電視片段，案件押後至明年6月再訊。<br />\n<br />\n17歲姓李的原告由他的父親代表入稟，被告為由律政司代表的警務處處長，港鐵也是相關持分者。原告一方上周接獲港鐵通知，指已將831相關太子站的閉路電視片段交給警方。原告申請要求警方披露片段，並公開涉及事件的所有警方文件及報告。<br />\n<br />\n法庭將案件押後至6月29日再訊，預留一日處理原告披露資料的申請。<br />\n<br />\n原告控訴於8月31日乘坐港鐵荃灣綫往中環方向駛至太子站時，有警員在列車中，用警棍攻擊他的頭部並拘捕他。據了解，他頭部受傷要縫針醫治，入院留醫九日，目前也沒被正式起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374457&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374457%26refer%3DShare&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlph1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=53c41a5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374457%26refer%3DShare&h=40a7d678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374457&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"53625be6115f92128e7727d0c1581752f7f7cb0b","tid":1795640,"uid":53498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:19:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老母港共要告就光速咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97ab785f029e5196b3d9074d62809476e738fa6","tid":1795640,"uid":124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"其實點解成日都會押到咁後 好奇一問 但告手足既咁快上庭"},{"pid":"b376912bacfd225332d6c33570fff4f4e3b561d3","tid":1795640,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e97ab785f029e5196b3d9074d62809476e738fa6","tid":1795640,"uid":124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"其實點解成日都會押到咁後 好奇一問 但告手足既咁快上庭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"有險可守"},{"pid":"d7f506d6d45cf2e490afc7dfd822cc870dfec8fb","tid":1795640,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:27:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，2020年6月"},{"pid":"c48b1fec3aa16c28a88508aa02bca7a12720e4fa","tid":1795640,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T05:31:16.000Z","msg":"有咩方法可以逼佢早啲審"},{"pid":"79d3a83fba0e9b57e3ba26bc3931c8756bf533d9","tid":1795640,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"等緊出年6月前變無政府狀態，唔撚洗審<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dabc2e096f253e4e4748409bbc2dda8c02fc3bf","tid":1795640,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79d3a83fba0e9b57e3ba26bc3931c8756bf533d9","tid":1795640,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"等緊出年6月前變無政府狀態，唔撚洗審<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"根本個法庭多膠餘<br />\n<br />\n而家只淪為比班狗拎嚟屈市民嘅工具"}]}